message:
MeeGo Summit FI // April 15-16th 2011 // Tampere, Finland

Join the world’s first national MeeGo summit in Tampere, on April 15-16th 2011. MeeGo Summit FI is a developer oriented 2-day summit packed with MeeGo and Qt sessions and showcases.

MeeGo Summit FI has plenaries, three tracks, Meegathon competition, party, technology demos, hacking space etc. Speakers include MeeGo, Qt and open source world’s top names such as Valtteri Halla, Carsten Munk, Thiago Macieira and Dave Neary.

Event is free of charge. The amount of seats is limited so please register quickly at http://summit.meegonetwork.fi.

Event is organized by COSS/Hermia Ltd and MeeGo Network Finland.

Welcome!
